### Random Short URL
POST http://localhost:5000/api/url/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "originalUrl": "https://www.whatsapp.com"
}

### Custom Short URL
POST http://localhost:5000/api/url/custom
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "originalUrl": "https://www.google.com",
  "customCode": "google167r"
}

### Redirect Short URL
GET http://localhost:5000/<shortId>

### Analytics for Short URL
GET http://localhost:5000/api/url/<shortId>/analytics
